Bootstrap: docker-daemon
From: nnclinssoap/scrnaseq-spatialxenium:4.5.2

%labels
    maintainer zemw@novonordisk.com
    description R environment for spatial transcriptomics: presto, argparser, arrow, spatstat
    version 4.5.2

%environment
    export LC_ALL=C
    export PATH=/usr/local/bin:$PATH
    export R_LIBS_USER=/usr/local/lib/R/site-library

%runscript
    exec R "$@"

%help
    Spatial Xenium environment (R 4.5.2, Bioconductor 3.22)
    Key packages: presto, Seurat 5.1, argparser, arrow, spatstat, ggExtra
    Built from Docker image nnclinssoap/scrnaseq-spatialxenium:4.5.2

    Usage:
        apptainer exec spatialxenium.sif Rscript your_script.R
